SUMMARY:Art Adventures (Morning Session)
DESCRIPTION:In this art-inspired\, hands-on art-making class for six- to nine-year-olds\, participants will create their own artwork inspired by the art on view in the Ackland galleries. \nSpace is limited; registration required below. Free for Ackland Members at the Household Level and above; $5 per child for all others.
